<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Hub Drogamais – Login</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Acesso centralizado às intranets Drogamais. Faça login uma única vez." />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="font-sans">
  <div class="flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,_#ffdede,_#f4f6f9_55%)] px-6">
    <div class="grid w-full max-w-5xl overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] bg-white shadow-panel lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]">

      <section class="hidden bg-sid-700 px-10 py-12 text-white lg:block">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-red-100">Drogamais</p>
        <h1 class="mt-6 max-w-sm text-5xl font-black leading-tight">Hub Central de Intranets Drogamais</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-md text-base text-red-50/90">
          Acesso unificado (SSO). Faça login uma única vez e acesse o SID, Campanhas, Auditoria e ferramentas sem precisar de novas senhas.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="px-8 py-10 sm:px-12">
        <div class="mb-10">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sid-600 text-xl font-bold text-white">HUB</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-ink">Entrar</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Acesso por e-mail centralizado da Drogamais.</p>
        </div>

        <form id="loginForm" class="space-y-5">
          <div>
            <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-600">E-mail</label>
            <input
              id="emailInput"
              type="email"
              required
              class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 outline-none transition focus:border-sid-500 focus:bg-white"
              placeholder="Digite seu e-mail"
              autocomplete="username"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-600">Senha</label>
            <input
              id="passwordInput"
              type="password"
              required
              class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 outline-none transition focus:border-sid-500 focus:bg-white"
              placeholder="Digite sua senha"
              autocomplete="current-password"
            />
          </div>

          <div id="errorBox" class="hidden rounded-2xl bg-red-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-red-700"></div>

          <button
            id="submitBtn"
            type="submit"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl bg-sid-600 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-sid-700 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-70"
          >
            Entrar
          </button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/public/js/auth-shared.js"></script>
  <script src="/public/js/login.js"></script>
</body>
</html>